PART: Interface
NAME: Interface
STATUS: draft

STRUCTURE: Dashboard
MARKER: dashboard
INTENT: provides an overview of the budget and transactions
---
The page has a header with the site title, a main section displaying the total budget and remaining balance, and a list of transactions with categories and amounts.

STRUCTURE: TransactionInput
MARKER: transaction_input
INTENT: allows the user to add a new transaction
---
The page has a form with labels for transaction description, amount, category, and date. There is also a button to submit the new transaction.
---PART---

PART: BudgetTracker
NAME: Budgettracker
STATUS: draft

STATE: Budget Data
MARKER: budget_data
INTENT: holds the user's budget and transactions
---
The app holds a user budget and a list of transactions. Each transaction has a description, amount, category, and date.
---PART---

PART: Actions
NAME: Actions
STATUS: draft

WHEN: Submit New Transaction
MARKER: submit_transaction
INTENT: adds a new transaction to the budget data
---
When the user submits a new transaction, it is added to the list of transactions and the total budget and remaining balance are updated.